s servicios en la nube y los contenedores ligeros docker restaurar todo su sistema será cuestión de minutos.\r\n                </p>\r\n\r\n            </article>\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <!--\r\n        \r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n            \r\n<article>\r\n                \r\n<h2>\r\n                    <a class=\"link\" href=\"https://youtu.be/vpB4jCYSiQA\" target=\"blank\">\r\n                    Reconocimiento facial\r\n                    </a>\r\n                </h2>\r\n\r\n                \r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n                    Desarrollamos software experimental capaz de realizar reconocimiento de \r\n                    rostros a través de servidores propios o de terceros.\r\n                </p>\r\n\r\n            </article>\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        -->\r\n    </section>\r\n</div>','Servicios','','inherit','closed','closed','','90-revision-v1','','','2018-03-01 16:52:37','2018-03-01 16:52:37','',90,'https://onnasoft.com/90-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(109,1,'2018-03-01 17:00:31','2018-03-01 17:00:31','','Que es el desarrollo Web?','','inherit','closed','closed','','85-revision-v1','','','2018-03-01 17:00:31','2018-03-01 17:00:31','',85,'https://onnasoft.com/85-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(112,1,'2018-03-01 17:12:25','2018-03-01 17:12:25','','Inicio','','publish','closed','closed','','inicio','','','2018-03-01 19:22:43','2018-03-01 19:22:43','',0,'https://onnasoft.com/?p=112',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(114,1,'2018-03-01 17:12:25','2018-03-01 17:12:25',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','114','','','2018-03-01 19:22:43','2018-03-01 19:22:43','',0,'https://onnasoft.com/?p=114',9,'nav_menu_item','',0),(117,1,'2018-03-01 17:18:02','2018-03-01 17:18:02','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-144\" style=\"float: right;\" src=\"https://onnasoft.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/season-1985856_1280-300x214.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"466\" height=\"332\" />\r\nNos enfocamos 